    <summaries>
      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Social Security Disability Fairness Act of 2016 </b></p> <p> This bill amends title II (Old Age, Survivors and Disability Insurance) of the Social Security Act to prescribe formulae for payment of Social Security Disability Insurance benefits over a period of 24 consecutive calendar months for individuals determined to be under a disability upon submission of a diagnosis of a terminal illness.</p>]]></text>
